@GenUI_HostAddress = http://localhost:5176
@OpenAI_Key = YOUR_OPENAI_API_KEY_HERE

### Health Check
GET {{GenUI_HostAddress}}/health

### API Info
GET {{GenUI_HostAddress}}/

### Chat Completion (Non-streaming) - OpenAI
POST {{GenUI_HostAddress}}/v1/chat/completions
Content-Type: application/json
X-LLM-API-Key: {{OpenAI_Key}}
X-LLM-Provider: openai

{
  "model": "gpt-4o-mini",
  "messages": [
    {"role": "user", "content": "Show me the weather in Tokyo"}
  ],
  "stream": false,
  "temperature": 0.7
}

### Chat Completion (Streaming) - OpenAI
POST {{GenUI_HostAddress}}/v1/chat/completions
Content-Type: application/json
X-LLM-API-Key: {{OpenAI_Key}}
X-LLM-Provider: openai

{
  "model": "gpt-4o-mini",
  "messages": [
    {"role": "user", "content": "Show me a comparison of top 5 programming languages by popularity"}
  ],
  "stream": true
}

### Chat Completion with Table Request
POST {{GenUI_HostAddress}}/v1/chat/completions
Content-Type: application/json
X-LLM-API-Key: {{OpenAI_Key}}

{
  "model": "gpt-4o-mini",
  "messages": [
    {"role": "user", "content": "Create a table showing the quarterly revenue for a sample company"}
  ],
  "stream": false
}

### Chat Completion with Form Request
POST {{GenUI_HostAddress}}/v1/chat/completions
Content-Type: application/json
X-LLM-API-Key: {{OpenAI_Key}}

{
  "model": "gpt-4o-mini",
  "messages": [
    {"role": "user", "content": "I need to add a new employee to the system"}
  ],
  "stream": false
}

